listurl = list()
listdf = list()
listres = list()

listurl[[1]] = "https://graph.facebook.com/v2.10/DoctorKoWJ?fields=posts&access_token=EAACEdEose0cBACIjX0pc0KurOA7F4ZBX6MphGjJOs1jSJdDldzrttoT8YfxPsHszNLpsjZAoyYHfziV6sNfchuF0j2oqhW3rCBzXOANHVvs2ULwDu6bktQxY0zKEiE5XjZBmHXZBJoVON7FMdVVOMk7oZCbBieheJ7QeAqKIwrZAV6ZAtIgU6CDeZBamYqbDk20ZD"
listres[[1]] = fromJSON(content(GET(listurl[[1]]), "text"))$pos
listdf[[1]] = listres[[1]]$data

for(i in 2:60)
{
  if(is.null(listres[[i-1]]$paging$"next")==0)
  {
    listurl[[i]] = listres[[i-1]]$paging$"next"
    listres[[i]] = fromJSON(content(GET(listurl[[i]]), "text"))
    listdf[[i]] = listres[[i]]$data
  }
  else{break}
}
fbdf = do.call(bind_rows,listdf)

4.Postong Time

fbdf$time = paste(substr(fbdf$created_time,1,10),substr(fbdf$created_time,12,19))
fbdf$time = strptime(fbdf$time,"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")
table.h = as.data.frame(table(fbdf$time$hour))
barplot(unlist(table.h$Freq),
        space = 0,
        border = NA,
        xlab = "Time",
        ylab = "Frequency",
        col = paste("gray",seq(20,89,3),sep = ""),
        names.arg = table.h$Var1)

5.Posting stability

fbdf = fbdf[order(fbdf$time,decreasing = T),]
dtime = vector(length = length(fbdf$created_time))
dtime[length(dtime)] = NA
for(i in 1:length(dtime-1)){
  dtime[i] = difftime(fbdf$time[i],fbdf$time[i+1],units = "hours")
}
fbdf$dtime = dtime
fbdf$month = months(fbdf$time)

fbdf.d = fbdf[1:length(fbdf$created_time)-1,]
stable.y = tapply(fbdf.d$dtime,
                  fbdf.d$time$year,sd)

fbdf.d = fbdf[fbdf$time$year>=114,]

stable.m = tapply(fbdf.d$dtime,fbdf.d$month,sd)
stable.w = tapply(fbdf.d$dtime,fbdf.d$time$w,sd)
stable.ym = as.data.frame(tapply(fbdf.d$dtime,
                  list(fbdf.d$time$year,fbdf.d$month),sd))
stable.yw = as.data.frame(tapply(fbdf.d$dtime,
                  list(fbdf.d$time$year,fbdf.d$time$w),sd))

6.Liks & Commemts

urlsum = list()
ressum = list()
like = list()
comment = list()

urlsum[[1]] = "https://graph.facebook.com/v2.10/DoctorKoWJ/feed?fields=likes.limit(0).summary(true)%2Ccomments.limit(0).summary(true)&access_token=EAACEdEose0cBACIjX0pc0KurOA7F4ZBX6MphGjJOs1jSJdDldzrttoT8YfxPsHszNLpsjZAoyYHfziV6sNfchuF0j2oqhW3rCBzXOANHVvs2ULwDu6bktQxY0zKEiE5XjZBmHXZBJoVON7FMdVVOMk7oZCbBieheJ7QeAqKIwrZAV6ZAtIgU6CDeZBamYqbDk20ZD"
ressum[[1]] = fromJSON(content(GET(urlsum[[1]]),"text"))
like[[1]] = ressum[[1]]$data$likes$summary$total_count
comment[[1]] = ressum[[1]]$data$comments$summary$total_count

for(i in 2:60)
  {
  if(is.null(ressum[[i-1]]$paging$"next")==0)
    {
    urlsum[[i]] = ressum[[i-1]]$paging$"next"
    ressum[[i]] = fromJSON(content(GET(urlsum[[i]]),"text"))
    like[[i]] = ressum[[i]]$data$likes$summary$total_count
    comment[[i]] = ressum[[i]]$data$comments$summary$total_count

  }
  else(break)
}

fbdf$likecount = unlist(like)
fbdf$commentcount = unlist(comment)
